		"description": "<p>You further upgrade your automaton. Its AC increases to 15, its hit points increase to 50, and you add one of the following options:</p>\n<p><strong>Antitoxin Module: </strong>The automaton gains three charges which stack with the ones from Autonomous Medic (if applicable). It can spend a charge to neutralize one poison with a DC of 15 or lower in a creature it can touch. It regains all spent charges when you finish a short or long rest.</p>\n<p><strong>Targeting Module: </strong>On its turn as an action, the automaton can highlight a target within 30 feet, granting an expertise die to creatures targeting it with attacks.</p>\n<p><strong>Flight Module: </strong>The automaton gains a fly speed of 40 feet.</p>",
